'''洗衣膠囊'''（或稱'''洗衣球'''） 是裝高濃縮[[洗衣粉|洗衣劑]]、[[柔順劑|柔順劑]]和其他洗衣產品的水溶性小袋子。洗衣膠囊的知名品牌包含[[Arm_&_Hammer|Arm & Hammer]]、[[Purex_(laundry_detergent)|Purex]]、[[寶瀅|寶瀅]]和[[汰渍|汰漬]]<ref name="cr">{{Cite web|title=Laundry detergent pods remain a health hazard|url=http://www.consumerreports.org/cro/2013/03/laundry-detergent-pods-remain-a-health-hazard/index.htm|accessdate=11 November 2014|date=March 2013|work=Consumer Reports|archive-date=2014-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141112041837/http://www.consumerreports.org/cro/2013/03/laundry-detergent-pods-remain-a-health-hazard/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。洗衣膠囊在2012年2月在[[宝洁|宝洁]]以[[Tide_Pods|Tide Pods]]<ref name=cr/>亮相而首次聞名。  

洗衣膠囊的化學成分跟液體洗衣劑一樣（包含[[alkylbenzenesulfonates|alkylbenzenesulfonates]]）。洗衣膠囊可溶解的膠囊外衣通常是以[[聚乙烯醇|聚乙烯醇 (PVA)]] 製成，或是PVA的衍生物。雖然化學成分大同小異，洗衣膠囊中可能有10%的水，而液體洗衣劑有50%的水。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.greenseal.org/Portals/0/Documents/Standards/GS-48%20Std%20Dev/GS-48_Background_Information_Laundry_Care_Products.pdf|title=BACKGROUND INFORMATION ON THE PROPOSED GREEN SEAL™ STANDARD FOR LAUNDRY CARE PRODUCTS (2012)|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=Nov 11, 2016|archive-date=2017-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329062623/http://www.greenseal.org/Portals/0/Documents/Standards/GS-48%20Std%20Dev/GS-48_Background_Information_Laundry_Care_Products.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[MonoSol|MonoSol]]是開發洗碗和洗衣用水溶性薄膜的其中一家公司，被包含[[汰漬|汰漬]]在內採用，年銷售額粗估為2億5千萬美元，佔有90%的市場。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chicagobusiness.com/article/20131207/ISSUE01/312079982/the-so-secretive-company-behind-tide-pod-detergent-packs|title=The so-secretive company behind Tide Pod detergent packs|newspaper=Crain's Chicago Business|access-date=2016-11-12}}</ref>這個薄膜被設計成在冷水中溶解。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.edentora.com/en_US/downloads/innovation/factsheet_Tide_PODS.pdf|title=Tide PODS Factsheet|last=|first=|date=|website=|publisher=|access-date=Nov 11, 2016|archive-date=2017-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329112553/http://www.edentora.com/en_US/downloads/innovation/factsheet_Tide_PODS.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根据市场研究机构[[尼爾森NV|尼尔森（Nielsen NV）]]的數據，[[洗衣膠囊|洗衣膠囊]]每年约占美國[[洗衣劑|洗衣劑]]市场70亿美元销售额的15％。洗衣膠囊广告是通过精确测量用量，来减少洗衣粉和液体洗衣剂浪费的一种方法。对于大量衣物，大多数品牌建议使用两个洗衣膠囊，而[[汰漬|汰漬]]建议最多三个洗衣膠囊。对于相同的衣物量，洗衣膠囊的成本要比液体洗衣剂高得多。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Tide's Answer To Slumping Sales? Use More Detergent Pods!|url=https://consumerist.com/2016/06/08/tides-answer-to-slumping-sales-use-more-detergent-pods/|accessdate=2016-11-12|date=2016-06-08|work=Consumerist|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021101058/https://consumerist.com/2016/06/08/tides-answer-to-slumping-sales-use-more-detergent-pods/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/three-tide-pods-a-wash-procter-gamble-pushes-more-doses-1465407495|title=Three Tide Pods a Wash? Procter & Gamble Pushes More Doses|author=Ziobro|first=Paul|date=2016-06-08|author2=Terlep|first2=Sharon|work=Wall Street Journal|issn=0099-9660|accessdate=2016-11-12|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326003620/https://www.wsj.com/articles/three-tide-pods-a-wash-procter-gamble-pushes-more-doses-1465407495|dead-url=no}}</ref>

